creator: Cerner Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Healthy Path is the new mobile companion to the Cerner Wellness Health Portal. Using cutting-edge technology, members can take a more active role in their health and wellness by conveniently tracking and managing data while on the go!

Key features include:
• Incentives – View incentive campaign information, track incentives earned, and complete Healthy Habits.
• Steps Tracking – View current and historical steps data.
• Physical Activity Tracking – View current and historical physical activity data.
• Wellness Assessment – Complete the Wellness Assessment questionnaire, obtain a Wellness Score, and view/edit responses following completion.
• Wellness Advisor – View health risk information after completing the Wellness Assessment.
• Screening Results – View current screening results data acquired from various sources.
• Events - View and register for upcoming events.
• Weight Tracking – View current and historical weight data.
• Connections – Connect or disconnect data tracking applications/devices.
• Goals – Access and define a Wellness Statement, daily steps goal, and weight goal.
descriptionShort: Healthy Path is the new mobile companion to the Cerner Wellness Health Portal.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New Features and General Improvements:

- Change the site you wish to visit with the new site search feature.

We're always making changes and improvements to our app to ensure we are providing a more meaningful and engaging workflow as you manage your health. Thank you for helping us continue to improve your experience. Download the latest version to see our exciting new updates!
